  74,5,"Wo…ó…óito-…óaa e rewugol sanamu."
  74,6,"Wata a okkiri fii Joomi maa …ìeydoraa …óen golle maa ko …ìuri heewde."
  74,7,"Mu√±√±or fii Allah, e kala lorra ko he…ìata maa."
  74,8,"Si wuttoyaama …ói…ómun ka allaandu."
