  74,10,"E hoore …ìen yeddu…ìe Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, nde wanaa newiinde."
  74,11,"An Nulaa…óo, accidam e mo Mi tagi on ka√±un tun, ka teege yumma makko, fewndo nde o alaano jawdi e …ìi…ó…ìe, on woni Waliid ibn al-Mughiirah."
  74,12,"Mi ye…ói mo jawdi …óuu…óundi."
  74,13,"Mi wa…óani mo …ìi…ó…ìe wonndu…ìe e makko, tawdetee…ìe e makko tummbondire, …ìe seedataa e makko fii setagol, hakkee ko o …óuu…óiraa jawdi."
  74,14,"Mi ya√±√±ani mo nguurndam e arsike e …ìi…ó…ìe, ya√±√±udee."
  74,15,"Refti e hoore keeferaaku makko ngun, himo tam∆¥inoo nde mi …ìeydanta mo e hoore …óum."
  74,16,"Wanaa no o sikkiri non ! Tawde o wonuno sanndal…óii…óo e Aayeeje Amen jippinaa…óe e Nulaa…óo Amen on, o woni feenu…óo …óe."
  74,17,"Aaray nde Mi fawata mo lette sattu…óe, …óe o hattanoytaa ronnditagol."